  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the hypothesis that the use of pediatric size phlebotomy tubes&#xD;
      reduces red blood cell (RBC) transfusions in adult intensive care unit (ICU) patients&#xD;
      compared with the use of adult size tubes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
